<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 18 Jun 2026 14:41:44 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>股价暴跌 90% 后加密货币金库梦想破灭</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-18/the-crypto-treasury-dream-unravels-after-a-90-stock-plunge</link><description>成立一家上市公司购买加密货币的商业模式正在崩溃。结果，在极其不友好的市场背景下，那些排队通过空白支票公司这样做的人面临着来自投资者的压力。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iXYhaoOKrSL0/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jun 2026 13:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-18/the-crypto-treasury-dream-unravels-after-a-90-stock-plunge</guid></item><item><title>新加坡将加密货币公司 Bybit 添加到投资者警报名单中</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-18/singapore-adds-crypto-firm-bybit-to-its-investor-alert-list</link><description>新加坡金融管理局周三将 Bybit Fintech Ltd. 添加到投资者警报名单中，以加强对未经许可的加密货币交易所的审查。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i1ncZrHTv82o/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jun 2026 09:54:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-18/singapore-adds-crypto-firm-bybit-to-its-investor-alert-list</guid></item><item><title>日夜交易：华尔街的文化变革</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2026-06-17/wall-street-avanza-hacia-mercados-24-7-por-presion-cripto</link><description>&lt;p&gt;传统金融实体开始评估各种资产不间断交易的模型，这种方式多年来一直在彻底改变加密货币领域的时间表。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iyQz9bOauOsQ/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jun 2026 17:16:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2026-06-17/wall-street-avanza-hacia-mercados-24-7-por-presion-cripto</guid></item><item><title>美国证券交易委员会废除数十年股票规则的提案有一个明显的赢家：加密货币</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-17/sec-proposal-to-scrap-decades-old-stock-rule-has-a-clear-winner</link><description>美国最高证券监管机构提议取消一项要求股票投资者获得尽可能最佳交易价格的规则，这将使金融市场的一个新的、不断增长的角落受益：加密货币。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iQdkeLml9WkI/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jun 2026 14:09:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-17/sec-proposal-to-scrap-decades-old-stock-rule-has-a-clear-winner</guid></item><item><title>Milei 的内阁首长声称自己是无人知晓的加密货币投资者</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-17/milei-s-cabinet-chief-claims-to-be-the-crypto-investor-nobody-knew</link><description>哈维尔·米莱 (Javier Milei) 总统最值得信赖的助手之一曼努埃尔·阿多尼 (Manuel Adorni) 上周声称，十多年前对比特币的全力押注为奢华的生活方式提供了资金，而这种生活方式现在正受到密切关注。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ic9Jh4.c20FA/v3/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jun 2026 13:11:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-17/milei-s-cabinet-chief-claims-to-be-the-crypto-investor-nobody-knew</guid></item><item><title>关于去中心化金融短暂而动荡的历史的重要阅读清单</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2026-06-17/defi-expert-eswar-prasad-s-essential-reading-list</link><description>&lt;p&gt;康奈尔大学教授埃斯瓦尔·普拉萨德的建议绝非学术性的。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ibECSrarfgqA/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jun 2026 11:00:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2026-06-17/defi-expert-eswar-prasad-s-essential-reading-list</guid></item><item><title>华尔街想要加密你的股票</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-17/nyse-nasdaq-and-crypto-firms-explore-tokenized-stocks</link><description>&lt;p&gt;该技术的支持者表示，将股票和其他资产放在区块链上可以使交易更快、更顺畅、24/7 可用。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iH9bs3CyX2LI/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jun 2026 09:00:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-17/nyse-nasdaq-and-crypto-firms-explore-tokenized-stocks</guid></item><item><title>代币化的下一个大难题：买家实际上能得到什么？</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-06-16/tokenization-s-next-big-conundrum-what-do-buyers-actually-get</link><description>创造流动性与创造经济价值不同。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ihwlbztcpY4w/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jun 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-06-16/tokenization-s-next-big-conundrum-what-do-buyers-actually-get</guid></item><item><title>币安为欧盟退出做准备，当地许可证悬而未决</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-16/binance-prepares-for-eu-exit-with-local-license-in-limbo</link><description>币安控股有限公司正准备停止在欧盟提供服务，因为获得欧盟运营许可证的最后期限即将到来，而且该加密货币交易所尚未获得希腊金融监管机构的批准。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ik0x1n3FXV_o/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jun 2026 14:17:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-16/binance-prepares-for-eu-exit-with-local-license-in-limbo</guid></item><item><title>华尔街每天都在关注加密货币风格的交易</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2026-06-16/wall-street-stares-down-crypto-style-trading-all-day-every-day</link><description>&lt;p&gt;传统金融公司开始接受一系列资产的全天候交易，这种方式多年来一直扰乱加密货币的时间表。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/is5NKju56qKU/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jun 2026 15:17:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2026-06-16/wall-street-stares-down-crypto-style-trading-all-day-every-day</guid></item></channel></rss>